<topic id="upgrading" >
    <title>Upgrading</title>
    <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords><indexterm>Installing Oxygen<indexterm>Upgrading</indexterm></indexterm>
        <indexterm>Upgrading Oxygen</indexterm></keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
    <body>
        <p>From time to time, upgrade and patch versions of <ph keyref="product"/> are released to
      provide enhancements that fix problems, and add new features.</p>
    <p product="author developer editor svnClient">
      <ph keyref="product"/> checks for new versions automatically at start up. To disable this
      check, <ph conkeyref="reusables-preferences-pages/open-the-preferences-page"/>, go to
        <uicontrol>Global</uicontrol>, and deselect <uicontrol>Automatic Version
        Checking</uicontrol>.</p>
    <p product="author developer editor svnClient">To check for new versions manually, go to <menucascade>
        <uicontrol>Help</uicontrol>
        <uicontrol>Check for New Versions</uicontrol>
      </menucascade>.</p>
    </body>
